{"data": [{"id": "4742257", "title": "AT&T's Meteoric Upside Isn't Over Yet", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Smart phone with AT&amp;T.com site in the pocket\" data-id=\"458421651\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"4256px\" height=\"2819px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/458421651/image_458421651.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">franckreporter</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>2024 has been a great year for shareholders of telecommunications conglomerate <strong>AT&amp;T</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/T\" title=\"AT&amp;T Inc.\">T</a></span>). Year to date, the stock is up 41.5%. And that doesn't even factor in returns from the distributions the business pays out. Since I </