ong/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Lynn Song</a></em></p> <h2>1 - What growth target will China set for 2025?</h2> <p>China's annual exercise of setting its growth target at the Two Sessions is extremely important as it sets the tone for government policy for the</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1322520591/image_1322520591.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742265-10-questions-china-2025", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 12:00:00"}, {"id": "4742256", "title": "Why I'm Downranking Patterson-UTI To Hold", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Drone captures a breathtaking sunset over the Permian Basin, showcasing an oil rig drilling and fracking for oil, amidst the vastness of the landscape\" data-id=\"1485934644\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1152px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">grandriver</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>After two acquisitions last year, (primarily NexTier in a 55% PTEN/45% NexTier combination, as well as technology company Ulterra), oilfield services company Patterson-UTI (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/PTEN\" title=\"Patterson-UTI Energy, Inc.\">PTEN</a></span>) bit the valuation bullet in 3Q24: it took write-downs of nearly $1 billion, reducing its accounting</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1485934644/image_1485934644.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742256-downranking-patterson-uti-hold", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:42:41"}, {"id": "4742254", "title": "JEPQ: Dissecting Its 10% Yield", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Percentage sign\" data-id=\"1692418614\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I am not a big fan of investments that promise high yields or returns. Almost always, there is a compromise in terms of risk or a fundamental weakness. I have explored some of these weaknesses in other covered-call ETFs I recently</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1692418614/image_1692418614.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742254-jepq-dissecting-its-10-percent-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 11:11:00"}, {"id": "4742251", "title": "Salesforce: Defiantly An AI Play And Mr. Market Agrees", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I must tip my hat to Mark Benioff and the team at Salesforce (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/CRM\" title=\"Salesforce, Inc.\">CRM</a></span>), as this is what a great quarter looks like. Time and time again, I have seen great companies sell off after delivering a strong</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742251-salesforce-defiantly-an-ai-play-and-mr-market-agrees", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 10:48:11"}, {"id": "4742250", "title": "SCHY: A Rare High Income Value Play Opportunity?", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"A world globe marked with several national flag pins\" data-id=\"1303046106\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"5220px\" height=\"3480px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Richard Drury</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>I covered Schwab International Dividend Equity ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SCHY\" title=\"Schwab International Dividend Equity ETF\">SCHY</a></span>) <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4685210-schy-the-international-version-of-schd-worth-diversifying-into\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4685210-schy-the-international-version-of-schd-worth-diversifying-into\" target=\"_blank\">in April this year</a> providing a broad overview of the fund and data from S&amp;P Global showing the fund's methodology historically has strong performance on a risk-adjusted return basis while</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1303046106/image_1303046106.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742250-schy-etf-rare-high-income-value-play-opportunity", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 10:44:54"}, {"id": "4742246", "title": "MSCI: Great Business, But Limited Upside", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Human hand uses a computer to find MSCI words.\" data-id=\"1398106287\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1081px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">WANAN YOSSINGKUM</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Overview</h2> <p>I spend a lot of time researching different industries and sectors of the economy. I started researching the Financial Services sector, and it quickly became one of my favorite places to invest. Some of my key positions in my</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1398106287/image_1398106287.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742246-msci-great-business-but-limited-upside", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 09:54:34"}, {"id": "4742244", "title": "Super Micro Computer: Sell The Relief Rally (Rating Downgrade)", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Data center server racks. IT modern hardware server room, data storage center, database information system. Hosting, it data backup, computing technology service, network security, supercomputers, 3D\" data-id=\"2148113350\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"988px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">quantic69</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p><strong>Note:</strong></p> <p><em>I have covered <strong>Super Micro Computer, Inc.</strong> (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SMCI\" title=\"Super Micro Computer, Inc.\">SMCI</a></span>) previously, so investors should view this as an update to my <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/author/henrik-alex/analysis?ticker=SMCI#hasComeFromMpArticle=true#source=section%3Amain_content%7Cbutton%3Abody_link\">earlier articles</a> on the company.</em></p> <p>On Monday, shares of beleaguered high-performance server and storage solutions provider Super Micro Computer, or \"Super Micro\" rallied</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2148113350/image_2148113350.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742244-super-micro-computer-sell-the-relief-rally-rating-downgrade", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 09:47:59"}, {"id": "4742242", "title": "Intel Upgrade: Made In America, Slowly", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Intel Corporation semiconductor company\" data-id=\"1729780233\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">tupungato</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>A new CEO could be a relief</h2> <p>The last time I covered Intel Corporation (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/INTC\" title=\"Intel Corporation\">INTC</a></span>), <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4585581-intel-im-hibernating-30-for-days\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4585581-intel-im-hibernating-30-for-days\" target=\"_blank\">I had just exited</a> the position and taken some tax losses.</p> <p>The gigantic strain of building out the US semi-FAB network was expending a lot</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1729780233/image_1729780233.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742242-intel-upgrade-made-in-america-slowly", "pub_date": "2024-12-05 09:33:23"}, {"id": "4742249", "title": "The Fall Of The French Government Means Less Growth And No Budget In 2025", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404884040/image_1404884040.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"French Flag on dark blue background\" data-id=\"1404884040\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404884040/image_1404884040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404884040/image_1404884040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404884040/image_1404884040.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1404884040/image_1404884040.jpg?io=g